      "content": "hey i just got off a 14 hour flight to dubai and my chest feels really sharp and painful whenever i breathe in deep. i'm also kinda short of breath. i've been super stressed with work lately and the travel is a lot... do u think its just a panic attack or something? i'm feeling pretty anxious about it.",
